OL,3,CHarry and Meghan to visit World
OL,4,CCentral Kitchen's Middle East
OL,5,Cheadquarters
OL,7,FThe Duke and Duchess of Sussex will
OL,8,Fvisit a worldwide organisation feeding
OL,9,Fpeople in moments of crisis during
OL,10,Ftheir second day in Jordan.
OL,12,FHarry and Meghan will travel to the
OL,13,Fregional headquarters of the World
OL,14,FCentral Kitchen where it co-ordinates
OL,15,Fand deploys a million hot meals across
OL,16,FGaza every day.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
