OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1772067788
OL,3,CHarry and Meghan to visit World
OL,4,CCentral Kitchen's Middle East
OL,5,Cheadquarters
OL,7,FFounded by chef Jose Andres, the
OL,8,Forganisation uses a network of field
OL,9,Fand community kitchens, bakeries and
OL,10,Fpartners to enable almost half the
OL,11,Fpopulation of Gaza to be fed.
OL,13,FThe Sussexes have travelled to Jordan
OL,14,Fat the invitation of the World Health
OL,15,FOrganisation's (WHO) director-general
OL,16,FDr Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesu to learn
OL,17,Fmore about the humanitarian effort to
OL,18,Fsupport the health and wellbeing of
OL,19,FSyrians and Palestinians who have
OL,20,Fsought sanctuary in Jordan over many
OL,21,Fdecades.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
