OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1772067788
OL,3,CHarry and Meghan to visit World
OL,4,CCentral Kitchen's Middle East
OL,5,Cheadquarters
OL,7,FThey will be joined by a WHO
OL,8,Fdelegation for a visit to the national
OL,9,Fcentre for rehabilitation of addicts
OL,10,Fas promoting mental health support is
OL,11,Fone of the themes of their visit.
OL,13,FThe centre, operating under Jordan's
OL,14,Fministry of health's national centre
OL,15,Ffor mental health, has a 40-bed
OL,16,Fcapacity and since its inauguration in
OL,17,F2001 has served as a short-term
OL,18,Fresidential and outpatient treatment
OL,19,Fcentre, offering medical withdrawal
OL,20,Fservices, psychological support and
OL,21,Fsocial counselling.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/4
