OL,3,CHarry and Meghan to visit World
OL,4,CCentral Kitchen's Middle East
OL,5,Cheadquarters
OL,7,FDuring their final day in Jordan, the
OL,8,FSussexes will visit female leaders at
OL,9,Fthe Jordanian Hashemite fund for human
OL,10,Fdevelopment, an organisation known as
OL,11,Fa pioneer in sustainable human
OL,12,Fdevelopment, and tour the King Hussein
OL,13,Fcancer centre.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/4
